  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the smoker to 225 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Season the lamb shoulder with garlic powder, salt, and black pepper",
    "Place the lamb shoulder in the smoker and smoke for 4 hours",
    "After 4 hours, brush the lamb shoulder with apple cider vinegar",
    "Continue to smoke the lamb for an additional 30 minutes",
    "While the lamb is smoking, mix the almond butter with chopped fresh rosemary and thyme",
    "Once the lamb is done, let it rest for 10 minutes before slicing",
    "Serve the sliced lamb with the almond butter mixture and assorted fresh herbs"
